      "icon": "https://keqingmains.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Thoma-Skill.webp",
      "details_html": "<div class='skill-section' style='margin-bottom:0;'>Thoma vaults forward with his polearm and delivers a flame-filled flying kick that deals <span class='pyro'>AoE Pyro DMG</span>, while also summoning a defensive <b>Blazing Barrier</b>.</div><div class='skill-section'><b>Blazing Barrier</b><br>The DMG Absorption of the Blazing Barrier scales off Thoma's Max HP. The Blazing Barrier has the following traits:<ul style='margin:0 0 0 18px;padding:0;'><li>Absorbs <span class='pyro'>Pyro DMG</span> 250% more effectively.</li><li>When a new Blazing Barrier is obtained, the remaining DMG Absorption of an existing Blazing Barrier will stack and its duration will be refreshed.</li></ul></div>",
